#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:164
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The KService cache generated by <command>kbuildsycoca5</command>. On "
#| "&UNIX; systems, <varname>cachedir</varname> is typically <filename class="
#| "\"directory\"><envar>XDG_CACHE_HOME</envar></filename>."
msgid ""
"The KService cache generated by <command>kbuildsycoca6</command>. On &UNIX; "
"systems, <varname>cachedir</varname> is typically <filename class=\"directory"
"\"><envar>XDG_CACHE_HOME</envar></filename>."
msgstr ""
"Der KService-Zwischenspeicher, der durch <command>kbuildsycoca5</command> "
"erstellt wurde. In &UNIX;-Systemen ist <varname>cachedir</varname> "
"normalerweise <filename class=\"directory\"><envar>XDG_CACHE_HOME</envar></"
"filename>"

